\toc1 God Ami Weng Miit Maakup Maakup Imi Kufatap-daa-laamin
\toc2 God Ami Weng Miit Maakup Maakup Imi Kufatap-daa-laamin
\toc3 Idx
\mt2 God Ami Weng Miit Maakup Maakup Imi Kufatap-daa-laamin
\s1 God ali kanolin:
\li1 \k 1. Atok God ami kanolin namti kala bom-bilip:\k* \xt Mak 10:27, Mak 12:29-30, Luk 1:37, Luk 6:35-36, Jon 4:23-24, Ap 14:14-17, Ap 17:22-31, Rom 1:18-23, Rom 11:33-36, 1Kor 8:4-6, 2Kor 1:3, 1Tim 1:17, 1Tim 6:15-16, Hib 4:13, Hib 10:30-31, Jems 1:17, 1Pit 1:14-17, 1Jon 1:5, 1Jon 4:7-12,16, Jut 24-25, Rev 4:8-11, Rev 15:3-4\xt*
\li1 \k 2. God ami Man, Yesus Kraist, ali kanolin: \k*
\li2 Yesus Kraist ali God ami man.\xt Mat 11:27-30, Mat 16:13-17, Luk 1:35, Jon 1:1-18, Jon 5:19-29, Jon 6:35-40, Jon 8:58, Jon 11:25-27, Jon 14:5-11, Jon 17:1-5, Jon 20:26-31, Ap 3:13-16, Ap 4:10-12, Rom 1:3-4, 1Kor 3:11, 2Kor 4:4-6, 2Kor 5:21, Gal 4:4-5, Fpai 2:5-11, Kol 1:15-20, Kol 2:9-10, Hib 1:1-14, Hib 7:26-28, 1Jon 2:1-2, 1Jon 5:20, Rev 1:12-18, Rev 19:11-16 \xt*
\li2 God ami Man kaali, Maria uta kuulula, tunum kesa. \xt Jon 1:14, Luk 1:26-38, Mat 1:18-25, Luk 2:1-20, Mat 2:1-23, Gal 4:4-5, Fpai 2:6-7, Hib 2:14-18\xt*
\li2 Yesus ayo unang tunum imi kukuyin-bam ale, yam-talal-bisa. \xt Mat 4:23-25, Mat 7:28-29, Mat 9:35-36, Mat 11:1-6, Luk 4:14-44, Ap 10:36-38, Jon 20:30-31\xt*
\li2 Yesus ayo kukup akal alik kusnum yaapkan imi nu-bisa. \xt Mat 8:1-15,23-33, Mat 9:1-7,18-33, Mat 12:9-14,22, Mat 14:15-32, Mat 15:22-28,32-38, Mat 17:14-18, Mat 20:29-34, Mat 21:18-22, Mak 1:21-28, Mak 7:32-37, Mak 8:22-25, Luk 5:4-8, Luk 7:11-15, Luk 13:10-13, Luk 14:1-4, Luk 17:12-14, Luk 22:50-51, Jon 2:1-11, Jon 4:46-54, Jon 5:5-9, Jon 9:1-7, Jon 11:11-44, Jon 21:4-6, Ap 2:22\xt*
\li2 Kamok kamok iyo Yesus ami dap-tal fuku-lomdup aalip taanak o, ke-bisip. \xt Mat 26:47-68, Mat 27:1-2,11-31, Mak 14:43-65, Mak 15:1-20, Luk 22:47-53, Luk 22:63–23:25, Jon 18:1-14,19-24, Jon 18:28–19:16\xt*
\li2 Yesus ami dabak as diim daa aasip. \xt Mat 27:32-56, Mak 15:21-41, Luk 23:26-49, Jon 19:17-37\xt*
\li2 Yesus dibi-din buluusip. \xt Mat 27:57-66, Mak 15:42-47, Luk 23:50-56, Jon 19:38-42\xt*
\li2 Yesus ayo asuk tam tiinala, malo ma iyo atamsip. \xt Mat 28:1-20, Mak 16:1-8, Luk 24:1-49, Jon 20:1–21:14, Ap 1:3-8, Ap 2:24-32, Ap 3:15, Ap 4:10,33, Ap 10:39-43, Ap 13:29-39, Ap 17:2-3,30-31, Rom 1:4, Rom 4:24-25, 1Kor 15:3-8,12-21, Rev 1:18\xt*
\li2 Yesus ayo asuk abiil tikin unsa. \xt Luk 24:50-51, Ap 1:9-11, Ap 2:32-36, Ap 5:30-31, Rom 8:34, Ef 1:20-23, Fpai 2:9-11, Hib 1:3-11, Hib 2:9, Hib 4:14-16, Hib 7:25-26, Hib 10:12-14, 1Pit 3:22\xt*
\li1 \k 3. Sinik Tambal ali kanolin:\k* \xt Mat 28:19, Mak 1:9-11, Mak 3:28-30, Luk 1:35, Luk 3:16, Luk 4:1, Luk 11:13, Luk 12:12, Jon 1:32-34, Jon 3:5-8, Jon 7:37-39, Jon 14:15-17,26, Jon 15:26, Jon 16:7-15, Jon 20:19-23, Ap 1:4-5, 8, Ap 2:1-18,38-39, Ap 4:31, Ap 5:3-5, Ap 8:14-17, Ap 10:44-48, Ap 13:2-4, Ap 15:28, Ap 16:7-10, Ap 19:1-7, Rom 5:5, Rom 7:6, Rom 8:9-16,26-27, 1Kor 2:4,9-16, 1Kor 3:16, 1Kor 6:11,19, 1Kor 12:1-13, 2Kor 1:21-22, 2Kor 5:5, 2Kor 13:14, Gal 3:2-5, Gal 4:6, Gal 5:16-18,22-25, Ef 1:13-14,17, Ef 3:16, Ef 4:3-4,30, Ef 5:18-20, Ef 6:17-18, 1Tes 1:5-6, 1Tes 5:19, 2Tes 2:13, Tat 3:5-6, Hib 2:4, Hib 9:14, 1Pit 1:2,11, 2Pit 1:20-21, 1Jon 2:20, 1Jon 3:24, 1Jon 4:13, 1Jon 5:6-8\xt*
\li1 \k 4. God ayo mafek mafek alik talalusa.\k* \xt Mat 19:4, Jon 1:3, Ap 14:15, Ap 17:24-26, 1Kor 8:6, Kol 1:15-16, Hib 1:2, Hib 11:3, Rev 4:11\xt*
\li1 \k 5. God ayo mafek mafek alik iyo tiin mosa.\k* \xt Mat 6:25-34, Mat 10:29-31, Ap 14:15-17, Rom 8:28, 11:36, Kol 1:17, Hib 1:3, Jems 4:13-16\xt*
\s1 Unang tunum ili kanolin:
\li1 \k 6. Unang tunum alik iyo kukup mafak fukulin.\k* \xt Jon 8:7-9, Rom 3:9-20,23, Rom 5:12, Gal 3:22, 1Jon 1:8-10\xt*
\li1 \k 7. Unang tunum kukup mafak ke-laabip kaali, iyo kala no-laabip.\k* \xt Rom 1:18-32, Rom 8:5-8, Gal 5:19-21, Ef 2:1-3, Ef 5:3-5, Kol 3:5-10, Jems 4:17, 1Pit 4:3, 1Jon 3:4-5\xt*
\li1 \k 8. Unang tunum ili ti kala no-lomdupla kawu, ban kemin umi maan uyo uktaayuk o.\k* \xt Mat 10:28, Mat 13:41-42, Jon 3:18-20,36, Ap 17:30-31, Rom 1:18-19, Rom 6:23, Gal 6:7-8, Kol 3:5-6, 2Tes 1:7-9, Hib 9:27, Hib 10:26-31, 1Pit 1:17, 1Pit 4:3-5, Jut 7, Rev 20:11-15\xt*
\s1 God ali unang tunum imi yim-buu-laamin kaami miit kaali, kalanolin:
\li1 \k 9. God ali unang tunum alik imi mok inayin-bamda yim-buulon o, kala-laaba.\k* \xt Jon 3:16, Rom 5:8, 1Tim 2:3-6, 2Pit 3:9, 1Jon 4:9-10\xt*
\li1 \k 10. God ami Man tunum Yesus Kraist ayo numi abiin kuluu-lomda taansa.\k* \xt Mak 10:45, Jon 3:16, Rom 4:25, Rom 5:8, 1Kor 15:3-4, 2Kor 5:19-21, Gal 3:13, 1Tim 2:5-6, Hib 2:9, Hib 9:28, 1Pit 1:18-20, 1Pit 2:24-25, 1Pit 3:18, 1Jon 2:2, Rev 5:8-10\xt*
\li1 \k 11. Yesus ami kiim kaata, numi ban kemin kaami uluum uyo kukan-tiisa.\k* \xt Mat 26:26-29, Rom 3:25, Rom 5:9-10, Ef 1:7, Hib 9:11-14, 1Jon 1:6-7, Rev 7:14-17\xt*
\li1 \k 12. God ali numi ban kemin iyo kukan-tiiya-lomda, lokonsa.\k* \xt Ap 5:31, Ap 10:43, Ap 26:18, Ef 1:7, Ef 4:32, Kol 1:13-14, Kol 2:13-14, Hib 10:17-18, 1Jon 1:8-10\xt*
\li1 \k 13. God ali numi talalu-yimulala kawu, ami tiin diim kaali tituun-kup tabin kesup.\k* \xt Ap 13:38-39, Rom 1:16-17, Rom 3:21-26, Rom 5:1,18-19, Gal 2:16, Gal 3:6-9, Tat 3:7\xt*
\li1 \k 14. God ali tiin kawong ilin alokso ma numi kuyinsa.\k* \xt Jon 3:1-16, Jon 5:19-29, Jon 10:10, Jon 11:25-26, Jon 14:6, Jon 17:2-3, Jon 20:31, Rom 5:21, Rom 6:5-14, Rom 8:10-17, 2Kor 5:17, Gal 2:20, Ef 2:1-6, Kol 2:13, Kol 3:1-4, 2Tim 1:10, Tat 3:4-7, 1Pit 1:23, 1Jon 5:11-13\xt*
\li1 \k 15. God ata nuli talalu-yimulala, almi man kesup.\k* \xt Jon 1:12-13, Rom 8:14-17, Gal 4:6-7, Hib 12:5-11, 1Jon 3:1-3\xt*
\s1 God ayo numi yim-buulon o kalba kaali, weng san-ilom kaal-kebup-kup dok nolokomup ma?
\li1 \k 16. Nuli ban kemin uyo, aket uluum kuluu-lomdup asuk daang ukuwum o.\k* \xt Mat 4:17, Mak 6:12, Luk 13:1-5, Luk 15:1-31, Luk 24:45-47, Ap 2:37-40, Ap 3:19-20, Ap 17:29-31, Ap 20:21, Ap 26:19-20, 2Kor 7:8-11, 2Pit 3:9, Rev 9:20-21\xt*
\li1 \k 17. Nuli ti Yesus ata-kup yim-buulokoma no kala titil-foko bom-bulup.\k* \xt Jon 1:12, Jon 3:15-18,36, Jon 6:47, Jon 14:6, Jon 20:31, Ap 4:12, Ap 16:30-31, Rom 3:20-22, Rom 10:9-10, Gal 2:16, Ef 2:8-9\xt*
\li1 \k 18. God ami kukup so, mafek mafek kanumin o kalba kaaso, kii itamon o kalap namti, God ami weng uyo tik-tiiman o.\k* \xt Mat 4:1-4, Mat 5:17-20, Mat 22:29, Jon 8:31-32, Jon 20:31, Ap 20:32, Rom 15:4, Rom 16:26, Kol 3:16, 1Tes 2:13, 1Tim 4:13, 2Tim 3:14-17, Hib 4:12, 1Pit 1:22-25, 2Pit 1:19-21, 2Jon 9-10, Rev 1:3\xt*
\li1 \k 19. Nuli ti wok-sam wokolum.\k* \xt Mat 28:18-20, Jon 3:22, Jon 4:1-2, Ap 2:37-42, Ap 8:12,36-38, Ap 10:44-48, Ap 16:14-15,31-33, Ap 19:1-7, Ap 22:12-16, Rom 6:1-4, Gal 3:26-27, Kol 2:12, 1Pit 3:20-22\xt*
\li1 \k 20. Unang tunum malo ma Kristen kesip iso maakup lotu kemum.\k* \xt Mat 18:19-20, Ap 2:41-47, Rom 12:4-8, Ef 1:22-23, Ef 4:11-16, Kol 3:15-17, 1Tim 4:13, Hib 10:24-25\xt*
\li1 \k 21. Unang tunum malo ma Kristen kesip iso maakup kominion inum.\k* \xt Mat 26:26-30, Mak 14:22-26, Luk 22:14-20, 1Kor 10:14-22, 1Kor 11:17-34\xt*
\s1 Nuli Yesus Kraist ami lak duu-lom ti kanolin ilum:
\li1 \k 22. Nuli Atok God so, numi Kamokim Yesus Kraist aso, alim imi weng kaata-kup weng san-ilomdup kutal-fukulum.\k* \xt Jon 14:15,21,23-24, Jon 15:10-17, Rom 13:8-10, 1Pit 1:14-16, 1Jon 2:3-8, 1Jon 3:22-24, 2Jon 5-6\xt*
\li1 \k 23. Nuli God so, unang tunum iso, imi aket kuya-laabup.\k* \xt Mat 22:34-40, Mak 12:28-34, Luk 10:25-37, Jon 14:21, 1Jon 5:3, Mat 5:43-48, Jon 13:34-35, Jon 15:12-17, Rom 12:9-10, Rom 13:8-10, 1Kor 13:1-3, 1Kor 16:14, Gal 5:13-15, 1Tes 4:9-10, 1Pit 1:8, 1Pit 4:8, 1Jon 2:9-11, 1Jon 3:11-18, 1Jon 4:7-21\xt*
\li1 \k 24. Yesus ami bom-bisa tap nokol kanola bomdupla yo.\k* \xt Jon 13:34-35, Jon 14:27, Rom 12:9-13, Gal 5:22-26, Kol 3:12-17, 1Tes 5:16-18\xt*
\li1 \k 25. Nuli ti beten-kup ke-bamdupla yo.\k*
\li2 Beten kemin kukup namti kala bombe: \xt Mat 6:5-13, Mat 7:7-11, Mat 18:19-20, Mak 11:24-25, Luk 11:1-13, Luk 18:1-8, Luk 21:36, Jon 14:13-14, Jon 15:7, Jon 16:23-26, Rom 8:26-27, Rom 12:12, Ef 2:18, Ef 6:18, Fpai 4:6-7, Kol 4:2, 1Tes 5:17, 1Tim 2:1-4,8, 1Tim 4:4-5, Hib 4:16, Hib 10:19-22, Jems 1:5-8, Jems 4:2-3, Jems 5:13-18, 1Pit 4:7, 1Jon 3:21-22, 1Jon 5:14-15\xt*
\li2 Unang tunum beten ke-bisip imi sang namti kala bom-bilip: \xt Mat 11:25-26, Mat 14:23, Mat 19:13-15, Mak 1:35, Luk 5:16, Luk 6:12, Luk 22:32,39-46, Jon 11:41-42, Jon 17:1-26, Ap 4:24-31, Ap 16:25, Ap 20:36, Ap 21:5, Rom 1:9-10, Rom 10:1-2, Rom 15:30-33, 2Kor 12:7-10, Ef 1:15-20, Ef 3:14-21, Ef 6:19-20, Fpai 1:3-5,9-11, Kol 1:9-12, Kol 4:3-4, 1Tes 3:9-13, 2Tes 1:11-12, 2Tes 3:1-5, Hib 5:7, Hib 7:25\xt*
\li1 \k 26. Nuli God ami yaap ke yo, kalin kaali God ami suunkup kukaala-laabup.\k* \xt Luk 17:11-19, Jon 6:11, Rom 1:21, Ef 5:20, Fpai 4:4-7, Kol 2:7, Kol 3:17, Kol 4:2, 1Tes 5:18, 1Tim 2:1, 1Tim 4:4-5\xt*
\li1 \k 27. Nuli unang tunum malo ma imi dong dakaayum o.\k* \xt Mat 6:1-4, Mat 7:12, Mat 25:31-46, Luk 3:10-11, Luk 6:38, Ap 11:27-30, 1Kor 10:24, 2Kor 8:1-15, 2Kor 9:1-15, Gal 6:9-10, Fpai 4:14-19, Hib 10:24, Hib 13:1-3,16, Jems 1:27, Jems 2:15-16, 1Jon 3:16-18\xt*
\li1 \k 28. Nuli unang tunum imi min lo tem kawu ilum o.\k* \xt Mat 5:3-12, Mat 18:1-5, Luk 14:7-11, Luk 18:9-14, Ef 4:2, Fpai 2:3-11, Kol 3:12-13, Jems 4:5-10, 1Pit 5:5-7\xt*
\li1 \k 29. Nuli moni so, bung so, kii kalanolin:\k* \xt Mat 6:19-21,24-34, Luk 12:13-21,32-34, Ap 20:35, 1Tim 6:6-10,17-19, Hib 13:5-6, Jems 2:1-9, Jems 5:1-6\xt*
\li1 \k 30. Nuli fit-bamdup din kot kemin baan diim kawu unemin dinim kemum.\k* \xt Mat 5:25-26,38-42, Mat 18:15-17, Rom 12:14-21, 1Kor 6:1-8\xt*
\li1 \k 31. Nuli gavman kiimi weng kaali ti weng san-kaamum.\k* \xt Mat 22:15-22, Ap 5:27-29, Rom 13:1-7, 1Tim 2:1-4, Tat 3:1, 1Pit 2:13-17\xt*
\li1 \k 32. Nuli ibakamin sinik ma imi beten kaa kamayin disa.\k* \xt Mat 4:10, Ap 17:22-31, 1Kor 5:11, 1Kor 6:9-11, 1Kor 8:1-13, 1Kor 10:1-22, 2Kor 6:14-18, Gal 5:19-21, 1Tes 1:9-10, 1Jon 5:21, Rev 21:8, Rev 22:15\xt*
\li1 \k 33. Nuli bis yokop kii numin disa.\k* \xt Ap 13:4-12, Ap 19:11-20, Gal 5:19-21, Rev 21:8, Rev 22:15\xt*
\li1 \k 34. Nuli saak olti kii anu-lom god ma ami kola-laamin disa.\k* \xt Mat 9:13, Mak 12:33, Rom 12:1, Hib 9:6–10:18\xt*
\li1 \k 35. Nuli sadikimin kukup kaa kanumin disa.\k* \xt Mat 5:27-30, Jon 8:2-11, Rom 13:8-10, 1Kor 5:9-11, 1Kor 6:9-20, Gal 5:19, Ef 5:3, Kol 3:5-6, 1Tes 4:1-8, Hib 13:4, Jut 7\xt*
\li1 \k 36. Nuli wok mafak atul tabin kaa, ina-lom weng mafak bakamin daa.\k* \xt Rom 13:13, 1Kor 5:11, 1Kor 6:9-11, Gal 5:19-21, Ef 5:18, 1Tim 3:1-3, Tat 1:7, 1Pit 4:3-5\xt*
\s1 Sios kaami kukup kaa kalanolin:
\li1 \k 37. Sios imi unang tunum kii kalanolin:\k* \xt Mat 16:13-20, Ap 2:41-42, Rom 12:4-8, 1Kor 12:12-30, Ef 1:22-23, Ef 2:19-22, Ef 4:1-16, Kol 1:18, Hib 10:24-25, 1Pit 2:4-10, Rev 19:5-10\xt*
\li1 \k 38. Sios kaami kamok kamok kii kalanolin:\k* \xt Ap 6:1-6, Ap 14:23, 1Tim 3:1-13, Tat 1:5-9\xt*
\li1 \k 39. Sios imi kamok kamok ili ti kalanola bomdiwa.\k* \xt Mat 28:18-20, Luk 22:24-27, Ap 20:17-35, 1Tes 2:1-12, 1Tim 4:1-16, 2Tim 2:1-26, 2Tim 3:10–4:5, Tat 2:7-8, 1Pit 5:1-4\xt*
\li1 \k 40. Nuli ti sios imi kamok kamok imi weng kaali, weng san-kaamum.\k* \xt 1Kor 9:14, Gal 6:6, 1Tes 5:12-13, 1Tim 5:17-22, Hib 13:7,17\xt*
\s1 Man alimal ili kalanolin:
\li1 \k 41. Imak so, kalel so, ili ti kalanolin:\k* \xt Mat 19:4-6, 1Kor 7:1-16, Ef 5:21-33, Kol 3:18-19, Tat 2:3-5, Hib 13:4, 1Pit 3:1-7\xt*
\li1 \k 42. Man kii kalanolin:\k* \xt Mat 15:3-6, Luk 2:51, Ef 6:1-3, Kol 3:20, 1Tim 5:4,8, Hib 12:7-11\xt*
\li1 \k 43. Awak-aalip kii kalanolin:\k* \xt Ef 6:4, Kol 3:21, 1Tim 3:4-5\xt*
\li1 \k 44. Unang kaluun kii kalanolin:\k* \xt Ap 6:1, Rom 7:2-3, 1Kor 7:39-40, 1Tim 5:3-16, Jems 1:27\xt*
\li1 \k 45. Nuli imak kelu, kalel kewa kemin disa:\k* \xt Mat 5:31-32, Mat 19:3-9, Luk 16:18, Rom 7:2-3, 1Kor 7:10-16\xt*
\s1 Kristen unang tunum iyo mafek mafek uluum tabin ma kuluu-laabip:
\li1 \k 46. Uluum tabin dukum uyo tiltam tabam-nokomu kaali, Kristen unang tunum iyo titil-foko tola-bomdiwa yi.\k* \xt Rom 8:18-25,28, 2Kor 1:4, 2Kor 4:16-18, Jems 1:2-4, 1Pit 1:6-9, 1Pit 2:19-21, 1Pit 5:8-10\xt*
\li1 \k 47. Unang tunum Yesus ami lak duulin dinim ita Kristen unang tunum imi yam-mafak-daalokomip kaali, Kristen unang tunum iyo titil-foko tola-bomdiwa yi.\k* \xt Mat 5:10-12, Mak 13:9-13, Luk 12:4-9, Jon 15:18-21, Jon 16:1-4, Ap 5:41, Rom 8:35-37, Rom 12:12-14,17-21, 1Kor 4:11-13, 2Kor 4:8-11, 2Kor 12:10, Fpai 1:28-29, 2Tes 1:4-8, 2Tes 3:2-4, 2Tim 3:10-13, Hib 10:32-39, Hib 12:3-4, 1Pit 3:13-17, 1Pit 4:12-19, Rev 2:10\xt*
\li1 \k 48. Kristen unang tunum iyo taan-laamin umi kukup uyo suun-daa-laamin disa.\k* \xt Jon 6:39-40, Jon 11:17-27, Jon 14:1-4, Rom 8:10-11,38-39, Rom 14:7-9, 1Kor 15:12-58, 2Kor 5:1-10, Fpai 1:20-24, 1Tes 4:13-18, Hib 2:14-15, Rev 14:13, Rev 21:1-4, Rev 22:1-5\xt*
\li1 \k 49. God ayo mepso kulu bomda dong dakaayinba.\k* \xt Mat 18:19-20, Mat 28:19-20, Jon 14:16-23, Rom 8:35-39, 2Kor 6:16-18, Ef 3:17-19, Fpai 4:13, Kol 2:6-7, 2Tes 3:16, Hib 13:5-6\xt*
\li1 \k 50. Setaan ayo yang yam-mafak-daalon o, kala-laaba.\k* \xt Mat 13:19, Luk 4:1-13, Luk 22:3-4, Jon 8:42-44, 2Kor 2:10-11, 2Kor 4:4, 2Kor 11:13-15, Ef 2:2, 1Tes 2:18, 2Tes 2:9-12, 1Pit 5:8-9, 1Jon 3:8-10, Rev 12:7-12, Rev 20:1-3,10\xt*
\li1 \k 51. God ayo titil-tibin dukum uyo Kristen unang tunum imi kuyilala, uluum tabin diim kawu yam-titil-diiyula, ili Setaan ami liip uyo bak-daa-laabip.\k* \xt Mat 4:1-11, Mat 6:13, Luk 22:31-32, Jon 17:14-19, Rom 8:31-39, Rom 12:12, Rom 16:19-20, 1Kor 10:12-13, 1Kor 16:13, 2Kor 12:7-10, Ef 3:20-21, Ef 6:10-18, Fpai 4:13, 1Tes 3:5-8, 2Tes 3:3, 2Tim 1:7-8, Hib 2:18, Hib 4:14-16, Hib 12:1-2, Jems 4:7, 1Pit 1:5, 1Pit 5:8-11, 1Jon 4:4, 1Jon 5:3-5, Rev 12:7-12\xt*
\li1 \k 52. Unang tunum sik umu-laabip kiili, God ata malo ma dong dokoya-laaba.\k* \xt Mat 4:23-25, Mat 9:35, Mat 11:2-5, Ap 3:1-6, Ap 8:4-8, Ap 19:11-16, Ap 28:8-9, 1Kor 12:9,29-30, 2Kor 12:7-10, 1Tim 5:23, 2Tim 4:20, Jems 5:14-15\xt*
\s1 Dok nolin mafek mafek ma tiltam tabokomu ma?
\li1 \k 53. Yesus ali asuk talokoma.\k* \xt Mat 24:29-44, Jon 14:1-3, Ap 1:10-11, Ap 3:19-21, Fpai 3:20-21, Kol 3:4, 1Tes 1:9-10, 1Tes 3:13, 1Tes 4:13–5:11, 2Tes 1:6-10, 2Tes 2:1-4, 1Tim 6:13-15, 2Tim 4:8, Hib 9:28, 2Pit 3:1-18, 1Jon 3:1-3, Rev 1:7, Rev 22:12-13\xt*
\li1 \k 54. God ayo unang tunum alik kiili, Yesus Kraist ami tiin diim kawu yim-bak-saanokoma.\k* \xt Mat 7:21-23, Mat 16:24-27, Mat 25:31-46, Jon 3:18-21, Jon 5:24-29, Ap 17:30-31, Rom 2:1-11, Rom 14:10-12, 1Kor 3:10-15, 1Kor 4:5, 2Kor 5:9-10, 2Tes 1:5-10, Hib 9:27-28, Hib 10:26-31, 1Pit 1:17, 1Pit 4:3-5, Rev 20:11-15\xt*
\li1 \k 55. God ayo dok kanolin unang tunum yim-buulokoma kiita, suunkup ilin abip kawu ilokomip.\k* \xt Luk 12:32-34, Jon 14:1-3, 2Kor 5:1-8, Fpai 1:23, 1Pit 1:4-5, Rev 4:1-11, Rev 21:1-4, Rev 21:22–22:5, Rev 22:14-15\xt*
\li1 \k 56. God ayo dok kanolin unang tunum yim-buulokoma disa kiita, suunkup as kiin-bam ilin abip kawu ilokomip.\k* \xt Mat 10:28, Mat 13:41-42,47-50, Mat 25:41, Luk 16:23-26, 2Tes 1:9, Rev 20:10-15, Rev 21:8\xt* 
